---
title: Jaye Hernandez
layout: layouts/base.njk
---
<img src="assets/plant-1.png" class="top-0 left-0 fixed hidden lg:block">
<img src="assets/plant-2.png" class="top-0 right-0 fixed hidden lg:block">
<div class="container-inner mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col justify-center">
  <div class="flex flex-col h-screen justify-center items-center text-center">
    <div>
      <h1 class="leading-none salt sm:text-8xl">hey, i'm</h1>
      <h1 class="leading-none sm:text-8xl">
        J<span class="salt">a</span><span class="swash">y</span>e!
      </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="text-xl mt-16 mb-5 lg:w-2/3">
      <b>I'm a full stack developer from the Philippines!</b><br>Grab a cup of coffee and read on.
    </div>
    <button class="py-2 px-4 bg-pink-200 rounded">
      Get in Touch
    </button>
  </div>

  <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col my-10 lg:m-32 justify-center">
    <h2 class="text-center flex-1">about</h2>
    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center lg:flex-row">
      <div class="md:w-1/2 lg:w-2/5 p-3 lg:order-last">
        <img src="assets/me.png">
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-3/5 p-3">
        <p class="mb-5">Hey, I'm Jaye! I like experimenting with new technologies, building small projects, and occassionally joining hackathons.

        <p class="mb-5">After graduating with a degree in BS Computer Science at UP Diliman, I joined <b>BeautyMNL</b> where I build new projects everyday I need to make this longer.</p>

        <p class="mb-5">In my spare time, you'll find me <b>editing photos</b> from a trip or listening to a musical non-stop.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col py-3 lg:p-16 justify-center">
    <h2 class="flex-1 flex-start">projects</h2>
    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center items-center lg:flex-row my-6">
      <div class="md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2">
        <img src="assets/letra.png">
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <h3 class="uppercase tracking-widest mt-3 lg:mt-0 lg:ml-5">Letra</h3>
        <div class="bg-pink-200 rounded-lg lg:rounded-r-lg p-5">
          Passively learn a new language every time you open a new tab. Published on the Chrome Web Store.
        </div>
        <div class="lg:ml-5">
          Vue JS
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center items-center lg:flex-row my-6">
      <div class="md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2 lg:order-last">
        <img src="assets/letra.png">
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <h3 class="uppercase tracking-widest mt-3 lg:mt-0 lg:ml-5">Letra</h3>
        <div class="bg-pink-200 rounded-lg lg:rounded-l-lg p-5">
          Passively learn a new language every time you open a new tab. Published on the Chrome Web Store.
        </div>
        <div class="lg:ml-5">
          Vue JS
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col my-10 lg:mx-48 justify-center">
    <h2 class="flex-1 self-end">blog</h2>
    {% for post in devto.posts %}
      <div class="">
        <div class="text-xl font-bold">{{ post.title }}</div>
        <div class="">
            {{ post.description }}
        </div>
        <div class="">
          {{ post.url }}
          {{ post.page_views_count }}
          {{ post.positive_reactions_count }}
          {{ post.comments_count }}
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
